\c 44
\s Jeremiya anoparidzira vaJudha vari paEgipita
\p
\v 1 Shoko rakasvika kuna Jeremiya pamusoro pevaJudha vese vaigara pa panyika yeEgipita, vakagara paMigidhori neTapanesi neNofi nemunyika yePatirosi, richiti:
\v 2 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsraeri: Makaona chakaipa chese chandakauisa pamusoro peJerusarema nepamusoro pemaguta ese aJudha; zvino tarirai, nhasi ava matongo, hapachina munhu unogara maari,
\v 3 nekuda kwekuipa kwavo kwavakaita kunditsamwisa, pakuti vakaenda kunopisa zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira, kuti vashumire vamwe vamwari vavasingazivi, ivo, imwi, nemadzibaba enyu.
\v 4 Zvakadaro ndakatuma kwamuri varanda vangu vese vaporofita, ndichimuka mangwanani ndichituma, ndichiti: Haiwa, musaita chinyangadzo ichi chandinovenga.
\v 5 Asi havana kuteerera kana kurerekera nzeve dzavo kuti vadzoke pakuipa kwavo, kuti vasapisira vamwe vamwari zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira.
\v 6 Naizvozvo hasha dzangu nekutsamwa kwangu zvakadururwa, zvikatungidzwa mumaguta aJudha nemunzira dzemumusha dzeJerusarema; zvino aparadzwa \add ava\add* matongo, sepazuva rino.
\v 7 Naizvozvo ikozvino anoreva seizvi Jehovha, Mwari wehondo, Mwari waIsraeri: Munoitirei chakaipa chikuru ichi kumweya yenyu, kuti mugure murume nemukadzi, mwana neanoyamwa kubva kwaJudha? Kuti musazvisiira anosara;
\v 8 pakunditsamwisa nemabasa emaoko enyu, muchipisa vamwe vamwari zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira panyika yeEgipita kwamunoenda kunogara sevatorwa, kuti muzvigure, uye muve chakatukwa nechishoorwa pakati pemarudzi epanyika?
\v 9 Makanganwa here zvakaipa zvemadzibaba enyu nezvakaipa zvemadzimambo aJudha, nezvakaipa zvevakadzi vavo, nezvakaipa zvenyu, nezvakaipa zvavakadzi venyu, zvavakaita munyika yaJudha nemunzira dzemuJerusarema?
\v 10 Havana kuzvininipisa kusvika zuva rino, uye havana kutya, uye havana kufamba mumurairo wangu nezvimiso zvangu zvandakaisa pamberi pemadzibaba enyu.
\p
\v 11 Naizvozvo anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsraeri: Tarirai, ndinorinzira chiso changu kwamuri pane zvakaipa, nekugura Judha wese.
\v 12 Ndichabvisa vakasara vese vaJudha, vakarinzira zviso zvavo kuti vaende kunyika yeEgipita kundogarako vari vatorwa, vachaparadzwa vese; vachaparadzwa nomunondo nenzara, vachafa nomunondo nenzara kubva kuvadiki kusvikira kuvakuru; vachava chinhu chinotukwa, nechishamiso, nechinomhurwa, nechinoshoorwa.
\v 13 Nokuti ndicharova vagere munyika yeEgipita, sezvandakarova Jerusarema nomunondo nenzara uye nehosha yakaipa;
\v 14 kuti kurege kuva neumwe wakasara waJudha, vakaenda kunyika yeEgipita kundogarako vari vatorwa, ungapukunyuka kana ungasara, kuti adzokere kunyika yaJudha, kwavanoshuva kudzokera kuti vagarekozve; nokuti hakuna ungadzokera, asi vakapukunyuka.
\p
\v 15 Ipapo varume vese, vaiziva kuti vakadzi vavo vanopisira vamwe vamwari zvinonhuhwira, navakadzi vese, vakange vamirepo, ungano huru, ivo vanhu vese vakange vagere munyika yeEgipita, naPatirosi, vakapindura Jeremiya, vachiti:
\v 16 Kana riri shoko rawakatiudza nezita raJehovha, hatingakuteereri.
\v 17 Asi zvirokwazvo tichaita shoko rimwe nerimwe rakabuda mumiromo yedu, tichapisira vahosi vokudenga zvinonhuhwira, nokuvadururira zvipo zvinodururwa, sezvatakaita isu namadzibaba edu namadzimambo edu namachinda edu, pamaguta aJudha nomunzira dzomuJerusarema; nokuti nenguva iyo taiva nezvokudya zvizhinji, taifara pamuviri, tikasaona njodzi.
\v 18 Asi kubvira panguva yatakarega kupisira vahosi vokudenga zvinonhuhwira, nokuvadururira zvipo zvinodururwa, takashaiwa zvese, tikapedzwa nomunondo nenzara.
\v 19 Zvino panguva yatakapisira vahosi vokudenga zvinonhuhwira, nokuvadururira zvipo zvinodururwa, ko taivaitira zvingwa zvokuvanamata nazvo, tikavadururira zvipo zvinodururwa, tisina varume vedu here?
\p
\v 20 Ipapo Jeremiya akati kuvanhu vese, kuvarume nokuvakadzi, kuna ivo vanhu vese vakange vamupindura saizvozvo, akati:
\v 21 Zvinonhuhwira zvamaipisa mumaguta aJudha nomunzira dzomuJerusarema, imwi namadzibaba enyu namadzimambo enyu namachinda enyu navanhu vese venyika, ko Jehovha haana kuzvirangarira here? Hazvina kufungwa mumoyo make here?
\v 22 Kusvikira Jehovha akakoniwa kuzova nomoyo murefu, nokuda kwezvakaipa zvamabasa enyu, uye nokuda kwezvinonyangadza zvamaiita; naizvozvo nyika yenyu rava dongo, nechinoshamisa nechinotukwa, isina unogaramo, sezvazvakaita zuva ranhasi.
\v 23 Zvamakapisa zvinonhuhwira, zvamakatadzira Jehovha, mukasateerera inzwi raJehovha, mukasafamba nomurairo wake, kana nezviga zvake, kana nezvaakapupura, naizvozvo zvakaipa izvi zvakakuwirai, sezvazvakaita zuva ranhasi.
\p
\v 24 Zvino Jeremiya akatiwo kuvanhu vese nokuvakadzi vese: Inzwai shoko raJehovha, imwi vaJudha vese vari munyika yeEgipita:
\v 25 Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsraeri: Imi navakadzi venyu makataura nemiromo yenyu, mukazviita namaoko enyu, muchiti: Zvirokwazvo, mhiko dzedu dzatakapika tichadziita, kuti tichapisira vahosi vokudenga zvinonhuhwira, nokuvadururira zvipo zvinodururwa; zvino chisimbisai henyu mhiko dzenyu, itai henyu mhiko dzenyu.
\v 26 Zvino chinzwai shoko raJehovha, imwi vaJudha vese vagere munyika yeEgipita: Tarirai, ndakapika nezita rangu guru ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha kuti zita rangu harichazorehwi nomuromo womunhu upi noupi waJudha munyika yese yeEgipita, zvichinzi: NaIshe Jehovha mupenyu!
\v 27 Tarirai, ndinovarindira ndivaitire zvakaipa, ndirege kuvaitira zvakanaka; vanhu vese vaJudha vari munyika yeEgipita vachaparadzwa nomunondo nenzara, kusvikira vapera vese.
\v 28 Vanopukunyuka pamunondo vachabva munyika yeEgipita vachidzokera kunyika yaJudha, vava vashoma vakasara vese vaJudha vakange vaenda kunyika yeEgipita kundogarako vari vatorwa, vachaziva kuti shoko richava nesimba nderani, rangu kana ravo.
\p
\v 29 Zvino ichi ndicho chichava chiratidzo kwamuri ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha kuti ndichakurovai panzvimbo ino, kuti muzive kuti mashoko angu achava nesimba kukuitirai zvakaipa.
\v 30 Zvanzi naJehovha: Tarirai, ndichaisa Farao Hofira mambo weEgipita, mumaoko avavengi vake, nomumaoko avanotsvaka kumuuraya, sezvandakaisa Zedhekia mambo waJudha mumaoko aNebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi, waiva muvengi wake, waitsvaka kumuuraya.
